http://ivf.com:80/cyclestu.html 206.185.60.251 19970123211931 text/html 7186
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Thu, 23 Jan 1997 21:21:08 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
Content-type: text/html
