<DOCHDR>
http://ivf.com:80/amenath.html 206.185.60.251 19970123213510 text/html 8964
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Thu, 23 Jan 1997 21:36:47 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
