<TITLE>General Information</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="#808FF">
<CENTER><IMG SRC="about.gif" ALT="About The Share Guide. . .">
<BR><BR>
<IMG SRC="colorb3.gif"></CENTER><BR><BR>
<P><FONT SIZE=4><B>The Share Guide</B> is a holistic journal and resource directory for people everywhere
interested in cutting-edge holistic health information. Our focus is on holistic health, environmental awareness and personal growth. We offer vital information for those interested in both personal and global health and healing. Our award-winning electronic zine has been on the web since October, 1995, and has been visited by over 52,000 people. See below to find out how to advertise your holistic service or product in our online Holistic Health Directory.<BR><BR>

<B>ABOUT <I>THE SHARE GUIDE</I> PRINT MAGAZINE:</B> <BR>With editorial quality, beautiful glossy covers
featuring unique nature photos, and polished graphic design, we have earned a reputation for integrity
and quality over 7 years of publication.  The Share Guide is available FREE to the public in Northern California at many newsstands and outlets in outlying areas; subscriptions available in the U.S. for
$8/year, or $12 outside U.S.

<H2>Publication Information:</H2> <IMG ALIGN=RIGHT SRC="photo.jpg">Published by <B>Dennis & Janice Hughes</B> in Forestville, California. Quarterly
release on January 1st, April 1st, July 1st and October 1st. 25,000 copies printed each quarter.
Magazine size is 8 1/2 x 11, approx. 100 pages. First issue published in 1989. Next issue theme (Spring '97): Travel & Retreats. <B>Deadline is March 4th; release date is April 1st.</B>
</FONT SIZE></P>
<H2>Editorial Information:</H2><FONT SIZE=4> Each issue is organized around a different theme. Upcoming themes: Spring '97, Recreation & Retreats; Summer '97, Holistic Education; Fall '97: Massage & Bodywork. Editorial is, for the most part, supplied by our advertisers. Please do <B>NOT</B> send in unsolicited
manuscripts! For more information about our editorial policy, deadline and upcoming themes, please
contact the editor, Janice Hughes, by e-mail, phone or fax.</FONT SIZE>

<H2>Advertising Information:</H2><FONT SIZE=4> There are three ways to advertise with us. Two in the printed magazine:
1) display advertisements  2) logo listings in the magazine's directory. Sizes and prices vary for each;
contact us for more information. The third way to advertise is with  listings in our online <A HREF="dirlist.html"><B>Holistic
Health Directory</A> (only $20/ mo.)</B> Contact The Share Guide office for details.</FONT SIZE><BR><P></P>

<FONT SIZE=3><B>We welcome your inquiries. Contact us at <A HREF="mailto:share@shareguide.com " >share@shareguide.com</A></B>
<BR> 
<B>Snail Mail: P.O. Box 610 Forestville, CA 95436<BR>  
Phone: 1-800-555-9205 ext. 3766  Fax: 707-887-9071</B> </FONT SIZE><BR><BR>

