<A HREF="http://www.infinite.org/Naturopathic.Physician"><B><BIG>American Association of Naturopathic Physicians</BIG></A>- an excellent site devopted to Naturopathic Medicine.<IMG SRC="new_big.gif"></B><BR><BR>

<A HREF="http://www.halcyon.com/kway/"><B><BIG>Ancient Healing Arts</BIG></A>- an interesting and nicely designed site focusing on aromatherapy and essential oils.</B><BR><BR>

<A HREF="http://www.ayur.com/"><B><BIG>Ayurvedic Foundations</BIG></A>- learn about many facets of Ayurveda, the ancient healing art from India.</B><BR><BR>

