<A NAME="Tachyon"</A><H1>Future Tachyon Energy Brings Better Health Today</H1>
<H3>by Coleen Rehm</H3>
<IMG SRC="rbline.gif">
<BR><BR><FONT SIZE= 4>

<P></P><I>"Physicists John Wheeler and Richard Feynman calculated that there is enough energy in the vacuum of a single light bulb to boil all the seas."
</I>OMNI, February 1991

<P></P>I first heard tachyon energy mentioned on <I>Star Trek: The Next Generation</I>, little realizing modern technology had advanced so much that this space-age energy is available today. For over a decade now, people have reaped benefits from Takionic<SUP>R</SUP> Original Tachyon Products--for everything from pain relief and improved athletic ability to enhanced mental acuity. The list of top athletes, leading healers and other professionals who use these products reads like a modern-day <I>Who's Who</I>: Sheri Howard (three-time Olympian), Barbara Brennan, Dr. Gary Null (health advocate and author) and Curtis Sliwa (founder of the Guardian Angels) among others.
	<P></P><P></P>On a recent NBC television show, <I>The Other Side</I>, host Dr. Will Miller illustrated (to his amazement!) how wearing a Takionic¨ belt dramatically increased his weight-lifting ability in only minutes.
	<P></P><P></P>Tachyon energy exists naturally in space and in the air we breathe. It's an environmentally sound resource that's virtually impossible to deplete. The biggest challenge has always been finding ways to harness it for ready use.
	<P></P><P></P>Twenty years of research, development and testing resulted in the creation of a unique, highly complex, patented silica-ceramic composite (known as Optimum Resonant Materials<SUP>TM</SUP>) that can only be found in the Takionic line of products, such as Takionic belts, beads, wrist bands and insoles.
	<P></P><P></P>This unique compound of Optimum Resonant Materials<SUP>TM</SUP> simultaneously attracts tachyon energy and focuses photon (light) energy from the particular wavelength of sunlight that's essential to good health.
	<P></P><P></P>The most unique benefit of these products is their ability to restore order from chaos. Stress of any kind (pollution, poor diet, electromagnetic radiation, lack of sunlight) creates water clustering in the body, decreasing water's permeability through body cells, tissues and organs. 
	<P></P>This traps water in cells and tissues, resulting in poor micro-circulation that reduces the body's ability to absorb oxygen and vital nutrients, and remove toxins and waste products.
	<P></P>According to research done by Professor Toyoda at the National University of Shiga in Japan, Optimum Resonant Materials<SUP>TM</SUP> increase permeability and molecular organization of water in the body, breaking up large water clusters, to maximize micro-circulation and improve delivery of oxygen and nutrients through blood and tissues. Scientific research shows this results in up to 90% faster recovery from muscle fatigue, increased physical and mental well-being, and improved focus and concentration (20-30% increase in test scores in double-blind studies). These products also balance energy flows, contributing to the harmony and integration of various energy fields (physical to spiritual).
	<P></P>The benefits of this technology are individualized to those who wear them. For example, S. Priebe, a radiation therapist in Idaho Falls, suffered from a circulatory disorder (Raynaud's syndrome), a heart murmur and fibrosystis in both shoulders. Within an hour of wearing Takionic beads, she felt a warm flush and ". . .an incredibly relaxed, peaceful, light feeling. My heartbeat calmed and evened out. I'm able to exercise my arms and not suffer excruciating pain in my shoulders."
	<P></P>Dr. Andrew Ptak, a chiropractor with lumbar scoliosis, used a Takionic bead patch and his anatomically shorter leg straightened our in 5 seconds, lengthening to perfectly match his right! X-rays later revealed the curvature in his lumbar reduced 7 millimeters in one hour, and computerized muscle testing (using the Digital Myograph) showed all-over muscle improvement, but "the greatest improvement was with my lower back and hip--strengthened 528%!"
	<P></P>As Thomas Edison said, "The doctor of the future will give no medicine, but interest his patient in the care of the human frame, in diet and in the cause and prevention of disease."
	<P></P>These stories can give you an idea of the benefits you might reap using these amazing products. But to fully appreciate this technological breakthrough, you've got to experience if for yourself. 
<P></P><I>For more information on Takionic Products, see their listing under <B>Tools for Living</B> in The Share Guide's</I> <A HREF="dirlist.html"> Holistic Health Directory.</A>
