<A HREF="http://omega-inst.org"><B><BIG>Omega Institute</BIG></A>-Excellent site from the largest holistic learning center in the USA.</B><BR><BR>

<A HREF="http://www.nbn.com/jacob/ship.html"><B><BIG>Paper Ships Books</BIG></A>- A book and crystal store with an interesting site: articles, book & music reviews, news, links, etc.</B><BR><BR>

<A HREF="http://www.well.com/user/karil/menu.html"><B><BIG>POV Productions</BIG></A>-- health and environmental videos.<IMG SRC="new_big.gif"></B><BR><BR>

