<A HREF="http://www.wellspring.com"><B><BIG>Wellspring Media</BIG></A>- dedicated to providing information promoting the "total wellness" of mind, body and spirit through online services and video programs.</B><BR><BR>

<A HREF="http://www.mhv.net/~worldlight/bookshop/b.htm"><B><BIG>World Light Bookshop</BIG></A>- offering reviews, excerpts, articles, bios and more.</B><BR><BR>

