<h1><font color="#0000FF">About&#133;</font></h1>
<p align="left"><img src="images/SKBLOGO.gif"
alt="SKB Environmental" align="left" hspace="20" width="245"
height="114"><font color="#0000FF">Corporate Offices at:<br>
251 Starkey Street<br>
St. Paul, MN 55107<br>
(612) 224-6329<br>
(612) 223-5053 (fax)</font></p>
<p>&#160;</p>
<p align="center"><img src="images/bluerule.gif" align="bottom"
width="480" height="3"></p>
<p align="center"><a href="index.html-ssi"><img src="images/home.gif"
alt="Home" align="bottom" width="75" height="22"></a> <a
href="ABOUTNEW.HTM"><img src="images/newtxt.gif" alt="What's New"
align="bottom" width="75" height="22"></a> <a href="skbhist.htm"><img
src="images/HISTORY.gif" alt="Company History" align="bottom"
