</font></a><font color="#0000FF">(British Columbia, CA)</font></p>
<p><font color="#0000FF">Please feel free to contact us if you
know of other sites that we should consider listing here.</font></p>
<p><img src="images/WOODS.gif"
alt="__________________Trees_______________________________________"
align="bottom" width="660" height="29"><font color="#0000FF"> </font></p>
<p><font color="#0000FF"><font size="5">SKB Environmental is
proud to be a member of and supports:</font> </font></p>
<ul>
    <li><font color="#0000FF">National Solid Waste Management
        Association (NSWMA) </font></li>
    <li><a name="NADC"><font color="#0000FF">National Association
        of Demolition Contractors</font></a><font color="#0000FF"><br>
        16 North Franklin Street, Doylestown, PA 18901,
        1-800-541-2412, Fax: 215-348-8422</font></li>
    <li><a href="http://www.swana.org"><font color="#0000FF">The
        Solid Waste Association of North America (SWANA)</font></a><font
        color="#0000FF"> </font></li>
    <li><font color="#0000FF">Midwest Chamber of Commerce </font></li>
    <li><a href="http://members.tripod.com/~compost//index.html"><font
        color="#0000FF">The Composting Council</font></a><font
        color="#0000FF"> </font></li>
    <li><font color="#0000FF">Minnesota Waste Association </font></li>
    <li><font color="#0000FF">Minnesota Environmental Initiative </font></li>
</ul>
<p><font color="#0000FF">We believe that commitment to industry
leadership requires an active voice in addition to participation. <strong>SKB
Environmental</strong>'s staff serve on the Board of Directors of
NADC, on the Composting Council's Government Affairs Committee,
as president of the Minnesota Chapter of SWANA, and are members
of numerous other state and local technical and working groups
focused on issues relating to planning for, management, and
regulation of the waste industry.</font></p>
