<CENTER><H1> Wankel Rotary Combustion Engines (RCE) and Vehicles </H1></CENTER>

<P> Wankel RCE snowmobiles, outboard motors, hovercraft, and lawnmowers?
Mercedes?  Corvettes?  Diesel and hydrogen RC engines?  RC engines from
5 cc to 31.0 litres? They're here! <P>

<CENTER> <A HREF = "submit.html">Submissions welcomed</A>. Edited by <A
HREF = "../index.html">Alan Marr</A>. </CENTER>

<P> Two RCE demos (Java), 47 pages, 35 images and 40,000 words. <EM>
Pages can be read in sequence. </EM> Please use and bookmark <A HREF =
"http://www.monito.com/wankel">www.monito.com/wankel</A> rather than the
original best.com URL.

